<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
            
   <p>
      So <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>iti</foreign></supplied>, this charming and celebrated house of Laḷitāṅkurapallaveśvara<note>The lord <supplied reason="explanation">Śiva</supplied> of the Pallava <supplied reason="subaudible">king</supplied> Laḷitāṅkura <supplied reason="explanation">the charming sprout</supplied>.</note> has been made by the wise/skilful/pious <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kṛtin</foreign></supplied> Pallava king Laḷitāṅkura, whose name is famous in the world.
   </p>
      		
</div>
         
